General.Name: Thai Plastic Industrial (1994) Public Company Limited
General.Description: Thai Plastic Industrial (1994) Public Company Limited manufactures and sells plastic bags, wrappers, and containers in Thailand. Its products include polypropylene plastic bags, high density polyethylene, and PVC wrap films. Thai Plastic Industrial (1994) markets its products under the Makrook brand name. The company was founded in 1994 and is headquartered in Nonthaburi, Thailand.
